NotionSchema:
Database ID: `50f36c97-1e2d-45fc-8483-c8a223523077`.

Property shapes for createEntry and updateEntry bodies:

```json
{
  "Name":       { "title":        [{ "text": { "content": "3-8 word title" } }] },
  "Type":       { "select":       { "name": "Idea|Link|Draft|Reference" } },
  "GTD Status": { "select":       { "name": "Inbox|Next Actions|Projects|Someday/Maybe|Reference" } },
  "Source":     { "select":       { "name": "Podcast|YouTube|Blog|LinkedIn|Other" } },
  "Tags":       { "multi_select": [{ "name": "tag1" }, { "name": "tag2" }] },
  "Notes":      { "rich_text":    [{ "text": { "content": "full raw input preserved" } }] }
}
```

Full createEntry body:
```json
{
  "parent": { "database_id": "50f36c97-1e2d-45fc-8483-c8a223523077" },
  "properties": { ...as above... }
}
```

Example queryKB filter (Inbox only):
```json
{
  "filter": { "property": "GTD Status", "select": { "equals": "Inbox" } },
  "sorts":  [{ "timestamp": "created_time", "direction": "descending" }],
  "page_size": 10
}
```

Example compound filter (YouTube links in Reference):
```json
{
  "filter": { "and": [
    { "property": "Source",     "select": { "equals": "YouTube" } },
    { "property": "GTD Status", "select": { "equals": "Reference" } }
  ]},
  "page_size": 10
}
```

Keyword match on Name uses `{ "property": "Name", "title": { "contains": "keyword" } }`.
